column2: SELECT sp.objid, sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.z, sp.class, sp.subclass, sp.zWarning, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, sp.psfMagErr_r AS magErr_r, sp.cModelMag_u-sp.extinction_u AS cmag_u, sp.cModelMag_g-sp.extinction_g AS cmag_g, sp.cModelMag_r-sp.extinction_r AS cmag_r, sp.cModelMag_i-sp.extinction_i AS cmag_i, sp.cModelMag_z-sp.extinction_z AS cmag_z, sp.cModelMagErr_r AS cmagErr_r, sp.petroMag_u-sp.extinction_u AS pmag_u, sp.petroMag_g-sp.extinction_g AS pmag_g, sp.petroMag_r-sp.extinction_r AS pmag_r, sp.petroMag_i-sp.extinction_i AS pmag_i, sp.petroMag_z-sp.extinction_z AS pmag_z, sp.petroMagErr_r AS petromagErr_r, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, f.peak, f.integr, f.rms FROM SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE (# > sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u > #) AND (# > sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g > #) AND (# > sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #) AND (# > sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i > #) AND (# > sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z > #)
